NAME
    Plack::Middleware::QRCode - Mount QRCode image service on your Plack
    application.

SYNOPSIS
    basic configuration:

        use Plack::Middleware::QRCode;
        builder {
            mount '/qrcode' => builder {
                enable 'QRCode';
                sub {  };
            };
        }

    provide default options:

        use Plack::Middleware::QRCode;
        builder {
            mount '/qrcode' => builder {
            enable 'QRCode' , 
                type   => 'png',  # image types: gif, png, jpg
                render => {
                    size          => 2,
                    margin        => 2,
                    version       => 1,
                    level         => 'M',
                    casesensitive => 1,
                };
            }
        }

DESCRIPTION
    Plack::Middleware::QRCode provides QRCode image service for your plack
    application.

    When you mount QRCode service on /qrcode, make a request from
    /qrcode/your_qrcode_text?s=10

    "s" means your QRCode image size.

AUTHOR
